wmsLayer.name: GA0293_50m
wmsLayer.title: GA0293 50m
wmsLayer.description: This layer contains bathymetry grids collected over the Mentelle Basin, Western Australia on marine survey GA0293. Data is gridded at 50 metre resolution. The colour ramp for the WMS is stretched between 100-4200 metres water depth. The dataset can be downloaded at the following URL http://services.ga.gov.au/metadata-gateway/metadata/record/75235.
